### Create Subscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/sub
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "subscription_plan_id": 1,
    "start_date": "2025-02-01",
    "payment_method": "credit_card"
}

### Get Specific Subscription
GET {{baseUrl}}/sub/40
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get User's Subscription List - All
GET {{baseUrl}}/sub/user
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get User's Subscription List - Active Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/sub/user?status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Update Subscription
PUT {{baseUrl}}/sub/40
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "payment_method": "debit_card",
    "auto_renewal": false
}

### Cancel Subscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/sub/40/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Subscription Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/sub/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Upcoming Payments - Default 30 days
GET {{baseUrl}}/sub/upcoming-payments
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Upcoming Payments - Custom days
GET {{baseUrl}}/sub/upcoming-payments?days=60
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
